344
00:28:15,310 --> 00:28:18,130
Oh, you took another woman's umbrella.

345
00:28:21,750 --> 00:28:22,650
I see.

346
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:26,260
You've gained favor in front
of My Lord Huaiyang

347
00:28:26,790 --> 00:28:27,930
and won a battle.

348
00:28:28,790 --> 00:28:30,500
It's natural that others admire you.

349
00:28:34,550 --> 00:28:35,450
Dear,

350
00:28:37,960 --> 00:28:39,500
you must have misunderstood.

351
00:28:41,400 --> 00:28:42,650
I found it

352
00:28:45,160 --> 00:28:46,980
on our doorstep.

353
00:28:48,200 --> 00:28:49,450
It must be yours.

354
00:28:50,710 --> 00:28:51,850
How could that be?

355
00:28:54,360 --> 00:28:55,410
My umbrella

356
00:28:56,160 --> 00:28:57,370
is right here.

357
00:28:59,470 --> 00:29:02,100
Xizhou is full of umbrellas like this.

358
00:29:05,270 --> 00:29:06,130
Honey.

359
00:29:08,510 --> 00:29:10,650
Don't overestimate your cleverness.

360
00:29:11,510 --> 00:29:12,360
You might end up

361
