372
00:30:38,230 --> 00:30:39,340
I can't sleep.

373
00:30:40,640 --> 00:30:42,100
I want to hear you talk.

374
00:30:43,790 --> 00:30:45,690
Haven't I told you many times before?

375
00:30:46,120 --> 00:30:47,340
Tell me again.

376
00:30:52,070 --> 00:30:53,100
I've forgotten

377
00:30:55,470 --> 00:30:57,690
