380
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:07,060
Trapped in my heart.

381
00:31:07,680 --> 00:31:08,600
Burdened by worries.

382
00:31:08,600 --> 00:31:09,690
Completely lost.

383
00:31:11,310 --> 00:31:12,890
We are bound by marriage.

384
00:31:14,030 --> 00:31:15,500
