385
00:31:16,600 --> 00:31:18,210
I'm willing to trust you.

386
00:31:18,510 --> 00:31:20,170
Please be my eyes.

387
00:31:30,200 --> 00:31:31,740
So, honey.

388
00:31:32,270 --> 00:31:33,740
Please tell me again.

389
00:31:35,440 --> 00:31:36,650
What were we like

390
00:31:37,790 --> 00:31:39,100
in the past?

391
00:31:42,710 --> 00:31:43,890
I'm tired.

392
00:31:45,070 --> 00:31:46,580
I don't want to talk about this.

393
00:31:49,960 --> 00:31:51,710
You seem unhappy

394
00:31:51,710 --> 00:31:52,890
since you came back.

395
00:31:57,230 --> 00:31:58,990
I've encountered some

396
00:31:58,990 --> 00:32:00,370
unpleasant things.

397
00:32:01,120 --> 00:32:02,060
Why?

398
00:32:05,510 --> 00:32:06,710
There's nothing to rely on,

399
00:32:06,710 --> 00:32:07,740
nothing to trace.

400
00:32:09,230 --> 00:32:10,750
The enemy on the battlefield

401
00:32:10,750 --> 00:32:12,370
can be confronted directly,

402
00:32:13,710 --> 00:32:15,340
but now, the challenges are

403
00:32:15,880 --> 00:32:17,130
a hundred times

404
00:32:17,440 --> 00:32:18,370
harder.

405
00:32:22,360 --> 00:32:23,850
I shouldn't be telling you this.

406
00:32:35,230 --> 00:32:37,300
You can tell me.

407
00:32:40,120 --> 00:32:41,130
First,

408
00:32:41,710 --> 00:32:43,300
you won't feel oppressed.

409
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:45,020
Second,

410
00:32:46,270 --> 00:32:48,930
whether you're powerful or frustrated

411
00:32:49,600 --> 00:32:50,650
outside,

412
00:32:52,270 --> 00:32:53,740
you can enjoy my massage at home

413
00:32:54,790 --> 00:32:56,610
and act like a child at ease.

414
00:33:11,230 --> 00:33:12,740
Thank you, Miantang.

415
00:33:17,070 --> 00:33:19,170
Did you also thank me

416
00:33:20,200 --> 00:33:21,780
when I comforted you in the past?

417
00:33:25,030 --> 00:33:26,100
In the past,

418
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:29,260
we didn't open up to each other like this.

419
00:33:29,710 --> 00:33:30,550
Why?

420
00:33:34,470 --> 00:33:35,340
Because

421
00:33:36,360 --> 00:33:38,890
the affairs of the capital were very complex.

422
00:33:39,750 --> 00:33:42,500
I didn't have time to come home every day.

423
00:33:45,120 --> 00:33:46,650
If we didn't meet often,

424
00:33:47,200 --> 00:33:48,740
how did our relationship become so deep

425
00:33:49,270 --> 00:33:51,300
