to treat my illness?

426
00:33:55,230 --> 00:33:56,170
No.

427
00:33:57,030 --> 00:33:58,170
It's not that it wasn't deep.

428
00:34:01,200 --> 00:34:02,100
Dear,

429
00:34:02,960 --> 00:34:03,980
when you just married me,

430
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:06,580
you had to learn business every day

431
00:34:06,960 --> 00:34:08,100
as arranged by families.

432
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:09,730
We were

433
00:34:11,070 --> 00:34:12,210
respectful to each other.

434
00:34:13,760 --> 00:34:14,730
And then?

435
00:34:16,720 --> 00:34:17,770
Then,

436
00:34:18,590 --> 00:34:19,460
every day

437
00:34:20,840 --> 00:34:22,420
when I came home,

438
00:34:22,760 --> 00:34:23,900
I could see you,

439
00:34:24,470 --> 00:34:25,580
with dinner prepared,

440
00:34:26,240 --> 00:34:27,080
waiting for me.

441
00:34:29,760 --> 00:34:30,600
Honey,

442
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:32,290
