456
00:35:08,280 --> 00:35:09,210
Later,

457
00:35:11,470 --> 00:35:12,460
we hired

458
00:35:13,150 --> 00:35:14,540
a manager

459
00:35:15,150 --> 00:35:16,500
to help run the business.

460
00:35:18,110 --> 00:35:19,290
That way, I could

461
00:35:20,150 --> 00:35:21,250
come home every day,

462
00:35:21,720 --> 00:35:23,250
and have time to spend with you.

463
00:35:24,880 --> 00:35:26,210
We had a courtyard.

464
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:29,290
You liked to grow crabapple flowers,

465
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:32,330
so many varieties

466
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:34,020
that they could bloom

467
00:35:34,320 --> 00:35:36,810
from early spring to late autumn.

468
00:35:39,240 --> 00:35:41,330
I enjoyed sitting with you in the courtyard

469
00:35:42,630 --> 00:35:44,420
on windy days,

470
00:35:45,470 --> 00:35:47,810
drinking tea,

471
00:35:48,360 --> 00:35:51,020
